&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Customer Engagement&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Solution Design:&lt;/strong&gt; Develop and present tailored solutions, including network security recommendations, physical security deployments, cloud security and LTE implementations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Advocacy:&lt;/strong&gt; Act as a trusted advisor, articulating the value-added benefits of Verkada’s solutions, addressing objections and securing technical wins.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Collaboration:&lt;/strong&gt; Partner with Account Managers and Solutions Engineers to create and execute territory strategies that align Verkada’s solutions with customer needs.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tailored Communication:&lt;/strong&gt; Effectively present Verkada solutions to a range of audiences, from Executive Briefings targeting C-level executives to loss prevention managers and IT directors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Public Speaking:&lt;/strong&gt; Command large audiences by speaking at internal and external conferences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This role requires regular travel, estimated&amp;nbsp;to be more than 50%&amp;nbsp;of the time, including both domestic and international destinations as needed. The successful candidate must be comfortable with frequent travel to support business operations, customer and partner&amp;nbsp;engagements&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;team collaboration.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Leadership &amp;amp; Product Adoption&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Subject Matter Expertise:&lt;/strong&gt; Serve as the go-to authority on Verkada’s full suite of products, educating customers, partners, and internal teams on their features and integrations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Thought Leadership:&lt;/strong&gt; Stay informed on industry trends in security and IoT by attending and presenting at strategic conferences, driving thought leadership within the market.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Content Development:&lt;/strong&gt; Write technical content to promote Verkada’s products and capabilities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Advocacy:&lt;/strong&gt; You are a product expert, leading training sessions for partners, customers, and employees on the latest Verkada offerings.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Scaling &amp;amp; Enablement&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tools &amp;amp; Training:&lt;/strong&gt; Create scalable resources, such as industry best practice guides, to accelerate customer onboarding and deployment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Process Optimization:&lt;/strong&gt; Define success metrics and refine strategies to improve product adoption and customer satisfaction.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Developer Ecosystem:&lt;/strong&gt; Advocate for APIs, 3rd-party integrations and SDKs to enhance customer solutions and experiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sales Enablement&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
